Scrolling background color
==============

Change the background color on scrolling
--------------

You just need to write this code after jQuery inclusion:

  <script src="path/to/jquery.scrolling-background-color.js"></script>
  <script>
    $('body').scrollingBackgroundColor(); // for the entire page background
    $('#element').scrollingBackgroundColor(); // for the background of #element
  </script>
